Package: notifications
Type: Package
Title: Send Notifications Via Messaging Apps
Version: 0.0.1
Description: Simple wrappers around notification functions for Google Workspace Spaces,
    Slack, Pushbullet, Zulip, and others. Useful for notifying users upon completeion of
    long-running code (or of errors).
